&lt;li&gt;Apply previous experience with successful hit finding strategies to find novel chemical equity, including scaffold-hopping approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with in-house drug discovery team to ensure compounds are distributed in support of other disciplines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular project updates to Leadership and Project Teams that include relevant updates. May include in-depth SAR, ADME, and PK analyses.&lt;/li&gt;
