&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with FDA and ICH regulations and guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills, ability to collaborate with a multidisciplinary team and interact effectively in a fast-paced team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
